<paragraph blockId="41.[1395,2603,728,1589]" box="[1397,2336,1358,1391]" pageId="41" pageNumber="435">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1397,2097,1358,1391]" pageId="41" pageNumber="435">Movements, Home range and Social organization.</emphasis>
